            "answer": "<p>Our oven mitts and pot holders are made from <strong>100% natural cotton</strong>, quilted for durability and comfort. Each piece is <strong>hand block printed</strong> using <strong>eco-friendly dyes</strong>, giving it a soft, breathable, and sustainable finish.</p>"
